# The Livesov app now lives entirely in ./trackly-nextjs/
#
# Copy trackly-nextjs/.env.example → trackly-nextjs/.env.local (or .env)
# and edit there. This root .env.example is kept only as a signpost so
# that anyone who reads it knows where to go next.
#
# Quick start:
#   cp trackly-nextjs/.env.example trackly-nextjs/.env.local
#   $EDITOR trackly-nextjs/.env.local
#   npm run dev
